        "subject": "LU-0000 mdd: do not cache append/immutable flags",
        "message": "LU-0000 mdd: do not cache append/immutable flags\n\nmdd can use them directly in struct lu_attr as it's already\nloaded usually. this lets LFSCK to manipulate these attributes\nremotely using normal OUT mechanism.\n\nthis is a proto to verify the idea.\n\nChange-Id: I3e98eea90e11654020810ef92e1b7dbd77e1804a\nSigned-off-by: Alex Zhuravlev <alexey.zhuravlev@intel.com>\n"
